data.description: Amazing price for this mild fixer near I5 and Florin. 3 beds with 1 Full Bath and bonus 1/2 bath!! Dual Pane Windows with Central Heat and Air. The property has some updating including kitchen cabinets, granite counters and updated bathrooms. Backyard features fruit trees with a Chicken Coop, and several storage sheds. The Front and Back yards are a blank canvas waiting for your Green Thumb, A little TLC will make this one shine. It's a steal at this price, don't wait too long before it's Going..going...Gone!!
